Basic Installation
==================

1) Path of Libraries.
In order to compile this software you need to have CppUnit, Glib and Expat 
installed on you system.
Paths for these library are set in CMakeLists.txt file. By defaults, these
pathes are those of Debian/Ubuntu system. If you have an other system, 
please change GLIB_LIB_INCLUDE, GLIB_INCLUDE, EXPAT_INCLUDE and 
CPPUNIT_INCLUDE path.

Build in release mode:
launch cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALLATION_PREFIX=/usr/local

replace /usr/local by any other path you want to install

then launch:

make
make install
